# Math operations module
# This module provides basic math functions

function sum that takes x as Integer, y as Integer returns Integer
    return x plus y

function diff that takes x as Integer, y as Integer returns Integer
    return x minus y

function product that takes x as Integer, y as Integer returns Integer
    return x times y

function quotient that takes x as Integer, y as Integer returns Integer
    if y is equal to 0
        return 0
    return x divided by y
